Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}看東西得比較\NLooking on the bright side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}正向\Nof things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我可以跟上，只要我想\NI can keep it up if I try
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}想著那些機會\NThinking 'bout the chances
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我錯失\Nthought I had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}以為太陽一直都在天上\Nthought the sun was out this whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你知道我是一位魔女\NYou know that I'm a sorceress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你想要我也能夠掌權\NI can take control if you want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啥都不能取代此時\NNothing can replace this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啥都不能分離我們\Nand nothing can divide us right now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}是否原諒我\NWon't you forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我以前的生活？\Nfor my life before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,1650)}有好多還要做的事\NThere's so much still that's left to do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}是眼冒金星\NAm I seeing stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)}他們真這樣說？\Nis this what they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}我的生活\NLiving my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)}是虛度每一天？\Non the day to day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我知道我得跟上\NI know I gotta keep this up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}表演繼續\NThe show goes on
