Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個魔女\NI'm a sorceress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你感覺到沒？\Ncan't you feel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒在耍戲\NI play no games
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我自己\Nthis is the real me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要沒時間\NI'm running out of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,給愛情用\Nto fall in love
