Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你是否還對我畏忌？\NAre you still afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,2600)}我應該不會咬人，但...\NI'd say that I don't bite, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你知道是謠言\NYou know that it isn't true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}他們所言\Nthe things they say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}反正我們從沒機會\NWe never had a chance anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}你知道我有魔力\NYou know I've got magic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)}就說關鍵字\Njust say the word
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}看進我眼\NLook in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你心是我一切\Nyour heart is my world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你能否感到我心\NCan you feel my heartbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我是一切\Nit's on me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)}我是全世界\NI'm the whole damn world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我不在乎\NI'm carefree
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}而你知道我是一位魔女\NAnd you know that I'm a sorceress
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我爽我也能夠掌權\NI can take control if I please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}別想那些我的錯誤\NDon't think about the mistakes I've made
